You‚Äôre correct ‚Äî that error is because no physical OpenBCI device or serial port exists on your phone (/dev/ttyUSB0 can‚Äôt be found).
We fix this permanently by adding a software simulation fallback ‚Äî so the GRRFP + Rahul.ai system will run live even without hardware.
